OL,3,CNumber of civil servants sacked for
OL,4,C'withholding' key details
OL,6,FThe has sacked a number of civil
OL,7,Fservants after they withheld key
OL,8,Finformation from politicians, the
OL,9,FHealth Committee President has
OL,10,Frevealed.
OL,12,FIn an unexpected statement, Deputy Al
OL,13,FBrouard used a special parliamentary
OL,14,Frule to tell the States that a small
OL,15,Fgroup of staff knew about the
OL,16,Fspiralling costs of the hospital
OL,17,Fmodernisation project but did not
OL,18,Fshare the information.
