OL,3,CNumber of civil servants sacked for
OL,4,C'withholding' key details
OL,6,FThis meant politicians debated
OL,7,Finvestment for the development without
OL,8,Fbeing aware of the full facts: civil
OL,9,Fservants knew it would likely cost up
OL,10,Fto #30 million over the #120m budget
OL,11,Fthat was approved.
OL,13,FDeputy Brouard says these employees
OL,14,Fwere aware of the new estimate in
OL,15,FFebruary 2023 but did not share it
OL,16,Fwith the Health and Social Care
OL,17,FCommittee or other parties.
