OL,3,CNumber of civil servants sacked for
OL,4,C'withholding' key details
OL,6,FThe Committee were only notified in
OL,7,FDecember 2023 and briefed Policy and
OL,8,FResources on Tuesday 27 February 2024.
OL,9,FAll States' members were told on
OL,10,FMonday 11 March.
OL,12,FDeputy Brouard says they are currently
OL,13,Finvestigating the reasons and motives
OL,14,Fof why this happened and other senior
OL,15,Fstaff members were equally concerned
OL,16,Fthat this information had been
OL,17,Fwithheld.
