OL,3,CNumber of civil servants sacked for
OL,4,C'withholding' key details
OL,6,FIn replying to questions from States'
OL,7,Fmembers, he added: "There has been a
OL,8,Fsubstantial change of personnel. We
OL,9,Frely on services provided by the civil
OL,10,Fservice, we have been let down and I
OL,11,Fhave made it clear we won't be let
OL,12,Fdown again.
OL,14,F"Any staff who were made aware of this
OL,15,Finformation are no longer employed by
OL,16,Fthe States of Guernsey."
