OL,6,FDeputy Brouard says he will spend the
OL,7,Fnext few months looking at how they
OL,8,Fcan reduce the costs of the hospital
OL,9,Fproject but made it clear that they
OL,10,Fwill not compromise on the
OL,11,Fdevelopment's scope.
OL,13,FIf it is not possible to get back on
OL,14,Fbudget, he will return to the States
OL,15,Fto debate the best way forward and to
OL,16,Fask for more money.
